Test a infinite loop program and see how it affect other Arista processes :

Tested with heavy CPU time consuming program( infinite loop) on arista. This will run on some random core. It will consume 100% CPU. 
Since the test device I used is 7808, it has many cores. So SSH access to device & also running other processes are not affected. 
Other cores are used for other processes. 
 
top 
 
